{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "過去與現在的終點", "storyInfo": "戰爭結束前的最後時刻，堅強的無名卡特斯感染者行走在戰場上，試圖挽救更多的人，並最終走向崩解的結局。特雷西斯進入了源石內化宇宙。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>“宇宙”。</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>我們應當如何解釋這個詞語？數學、物理、信仰、空想——</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>我們窮盡思維，試圖用不同的語言模型描述這個依舊陌生的詞語，並傲慢地宣稱我們掌握了絕對正確的“知識”。</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>但為何毀滅真正近在咫尺時，大多數人卻又緘默不語？</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>知識是不可逆轉的。既然我們已從無數謬論中窺到了片面的真理，自然也無法安然退回到無知的黑暗中，漠視終結的降臨。</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>我想，也許我已經觸碰到解答終極問題的關鍵——</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<color=#000000>用我和你創造的語言，{@nickname}。</color>", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g5_crackedhispdwarship", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“Dr.{@nickname}，這場戰爭該結束了。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“那位德拉克點燃城牆的紫火極大地推動了戰爭的進展。當典範軍和公爵聯軍的隊伍推進至孽茨雷最後的陣地前時——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們停下這場戰爭的目的也終於觸手可及。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“但……凱爾希醫生，最後這短短的一段路還要花上多少時間？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“沒人能保證，阿米婭。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>倫蒂尼姆週邊戰場，“榮光”號殘骸</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石……", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些該死的源石真的斬斷了這艘旗艦。我必須留在這裡，加入這裡的駐軍繼續戰鬥……", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我不能繼續陪你往前走了，孩子。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一路過來，只有廢墟和那些死去的……我沒有看到任何駐軍。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，請不要叫我孩子！修道院的大家已經為我的成年慶祝過了——", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你的脾氣還真像我的女兒。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到那邊高處還閃著光芒的地方了嗎？那是開斯特公爵閣下的“榮光”號的一部分。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那門艦炮還在運作，說明我從廣播裡接收到的通訊是真的。我原先的隊伍既然隸屬開斯特公爵閣下，現在自然該歸隊了。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的傷勢……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#9$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有你幫忙治療，我已經能走得動路了。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是你，你確定要繼續往城裡走嗎？那是污染最嚴重的地方，活性源石環境會害死你的。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教爺爺說過，那位從礦場救下我的好心人為了送我回修道院，也吃了很多的苦，走過很多的路。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救贖從來不是毫無代價的，我很早就清楚。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心我，修士們教會了我很多避開危險的辦法。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我走到終點之前，只要能再多救一個人，任何一個人……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我從來沒有見過有哪一位修道院裡的修士像你這樣虔誠……謝謝你，維多利亞以你的善良為榮。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教爺爺說，信仰並不是為了一己的榮譽……懷有信仰的人，是虔誠地相信，善舉會將這片大地變得更好……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變得更好嗎……哈，或許吧。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但無論如何，謝謝你，小兔子，為你做的一切。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能最後幫我一個忙嗎，孩子？如果你回到了城裡，我的家還在，我的女兒……也還在……", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩告訴她，爸爸一直在保護著她。", "name": "疲憊的傷員"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞軍人努力抬起受傷的手臂，向卡特斯敬了一個不甚標準的軍禮，然後坦然地轉身走向遠處軍艦的殘骸，消失在源石的叢林裡。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯望著遠處艦炮上那抹淡淡的金光，不由得嘆了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處炮火正響，小小的卡特斯繼續向著天際線上的那座城市——倫蒂尼姆進發。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我也能聽到炮擊的聲音了，Dr.{@nickname}，凱瑟琳女士的'爬行號'已經在衝擊食腐者的陣地。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“但擊敗了食腐者就能結束戰爭嗎？還有那些被波及的無辜者……他們該怎麼辦？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們沒辦法在戰爭中救下每一個人，阿米婭。我們能做的，只有幫助倫蒂尼姆人更快地結束這場災難。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“那就意味著，食腐者並非是我們最後的難題。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>倫蒂尼姆無名避難所</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪麗、戴維，請不要把這個孩子藏在這裡的事情告訴其他人。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在城牆下遇到了他，他已經沒有其他地方能去。他的父母都是倫蒂尼姆人，他說，很久以前你們在公園裡見過面，不是嗎？", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.3", "scale": 0.85, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "80,0"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恐懼的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.9, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得了。但你幫了我們，我答應幫你忙。是幫你，不是幫他！", "name": "滿臉厭惡的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_240", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.3", "scale": 0.85, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "80,0"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你們。他只會躲在這裡，不會亂跑，也不會出聲。我保證他不會嚇到任何人。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（快速地點頭）", "name": "恐懼的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很快就回來，我答應了一個人，要找到他的女兒。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法在外面保護你，外面街道上到處都是充滿敵意的人——", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我也找不到更好的地方暫時安置你。至少，這裡許多人都接受過我的幫助，我相信這些孩子。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#10$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "30,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小薩卡茲緊緊抓住了卡特斯的手臂，卻摸到了那些尖銳的源石結晶。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "30,0", "posto": "80,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他下意識地縮回了手。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）對、對不起！我和爸爸媽媽在一起的時候……很少接觸感染者。", "name": "恐懼的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會回來找你的。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恐懼的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.9, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "滿臉厭惡的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.5, "to": 0.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "cg_smoke", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 60.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "卡特斯離開的時間並不長。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當她按照地址找到軍人的家時，那裡已經什麼都不剩了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但從廢墟中找到的信來看，軍人的女兒已經加入了城內一支反抗薩卡茲的隊伍——“典範軍”。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "卡特斯返回避難所的路並不好走，在維多利亞人聯合向聖王會西部大堂的薩卡茲陣地進攻時，城內被源石影響的區域仍在不斷擴大。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "還有那些四處流竄的狂熱薩卡茲傭兵，正彷彿失去了主心骨一般肆意行動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她感到頭痛，因為城內這糟糕的現狀，也因為她身體上那些糟糕的黑色結晶。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“或許，我也快走到終點了，主教爺爺。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問……剛剛是你們在那些傭兵騷擾避難所時保護了這些人嗎？", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。我們這支小隊裡典範軍和公爵聯軍的士兵都有，準備去聖王會西部大堂陣地時突然收到了求救。", "name": "興奮的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請相信，這場混亂馬上就會結束了。也感謝您照顧這些孩子和避難的人。", "name": "興奮的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，您在找什麼人嗎？", "name": "興奮的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我們順便也清理了一下周圍躲著的魔族佬，他們眼看快敗了，也想躲起來。", "name": "興奮的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再會，我們得趕去前線了。", "name": "興奮的軍人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒看到那個孩子。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……跟我來。", "name": "滿臉厭惡的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4, "delay": 0.3, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子帶著卡特斯穿過工廠層層疊疊的掩體，卡特斯看到避難所的其他人沉默地搬運著薩卡茲的屍體。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走到一堆貨櫃之前，孩子費力地挪開了凌亂的遮掩。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個蜷縮的薩卡茲孩子驚恐地看著他們。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她來了。", "name": "滿臉厭惡的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過幫你。剛才事情比較突然，我也沒有其他地方能藏他了。", "name": "滿臉厭惡的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他不能繼續留在這裡。", "name": "沉默的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……回來的路上我遇到了一支名叫整合運動的隊伍，他們可以收留這個孩子。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_mini01_westlobbysquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，那個孩子我們會照顧好的——但是你呢？", "name": "整合運動成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的感染狀況很糟糕……你應該和我們一起走。", "name": "整合運動成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……還有其他的事沒有做完。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我不會勉強你，你和我認識的很多同伴很像。", "name": "整合運動成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些抑制劑和防護裝備我留給你了。再見。", "name": "整合運動成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……再見。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1729_1#2$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處，維多利亞人前仆後繼地向食腐者之王最後的陣地走去，生命在消逝。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是她的戰爭，她感到恐懼，她也無法理解支撐這些人克服死亡恐懼的力量來源於何處。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她希望救下更多的人，繼續麻木地救下更多的人……一個又一個。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哪怕只是徒勞。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起離開修道院那天，主教與她坐在河畔教堂外的告別。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問，何為信仰？", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵……我年輕遊歷時曾去過伊比利亞，我親眼目睹過大靜謐下身邊人生活的崩潰，但那個頑強的國家卻從未徹底屈服。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起初，我只是在為那個國家的生命力而讚嘆，但隨著我活過的歲月越來越久，我才逐漸醒悟……", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的生命力，就是信仰。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有誰教育過我，或是其他那些伊比利亞人，我們應該何去何從？有誰曾許諾過，我們一定會跨過那樣恐怖的災難？", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，但我們總會在災難面前說服我們自己。我們經歷的一切總有意義，苦難終有盡頭，我們會有一個美好的未來。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是信仰。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰不在經文上，也不在禱告詞和讚美詩當中，而是在我們的生命中。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰在我們的身體和思維中，在我們的心臟的每一次律動中，在一呼一吸之中。是我們一切力量的來源。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只因為我們相信。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教爺爺。如果真如您所說，一切苦難終歸是有盡頭的，那個美好的將來，又在何處呢……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教爺爺……我應該，已經盡力了。", "name": "堅強的感染者"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i21", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "y": 80.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 80.0, "yTo": 55.0, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_airwaramb", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯疲憊地倒在廢墟中，聽到遠處傳來的炮火聲和隱隱的哭喊。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇烈的疼痛提醒著她這副身體已經行至終點的殘酷事實。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她向周圍那些被她從死亡前救下的人招了招手，獨自留在遠離其他人的空曠處。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crystal_shatter"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的身體開始崩解。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我願意去相信……", "name": "堅強的感染者"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯眼睛所能捕捉到的光越來越黯淡，直至陷入漫長的黑夜。"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i21", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後她看到似乎有人握住了她近乎破碎的手，光線開始重新湧回她的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_mini01_westlobbysquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，怎麼了？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line358"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#2$2"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好像聽到了，感染者發生崩解的聲音……又一次。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#2$2"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我幾乎都能遠遠看見離去的人最後時刻迸發的光芒，距離我們並不遠。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#2$2"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，我們已經見過太多次……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "走吧。;該去結束這一切了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line367", "option2": "line367"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們去面對特雷西斯。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line369"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，走吧。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line375"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "凱爾希，我突然有一個疑問。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line381"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "源石內化宇宙中的靜滯……到底意味著什麼？;我們曾涉足的那個地方，是不是連時間都無法逃脫？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line383", "option2": "line383"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "58_mini05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "資訊的浪湧衝擊著他，試圖將他吞沒。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但特雷西斯屹立不動。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 45.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我終於親眼看到了你創造的偉績，特蕾西婭。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>源石內化宇宙</><p=2>未知時間</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他抬頭望向矗立在虛空中的高塔，崩潰的碎屑重新化作無序的資訊回歸虛空。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯握住了飄散而下的碎屑，但手中轉瞬卻又一無所有。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為我打開了這扇門，最後這段路，我會替你走完，特蕾西婭。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奪下這枚屬於薩卡茲的源石，薩卡茲將第一次擁有自己主宰自己命運的權力。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他握緊了手中的劍，冷冷地注視著虛空中那逐漸靠近的巨大菱形。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨即，他走向了崩潰的塔。他很清楚，他將要面對的存在就在那裡。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毀滅些什麼，來鑄造階梯。特蕾西婭已為他留下了道路。"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“直至消散也未曾放棄抗爭的眾魂啊，在源石之中為薩卡茲做了最後一件事——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“為所有仍活著的人搏一個有權為平等生存而抗爭的未來。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“大家，向前走吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一如過往，你為我指引方向，我的劍會開闢前路。", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我未曾食言，特蕾西婭——", "name": "特雷西斯"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走上了階梯，走向了瀕臨崩毀的塔之巔。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}